---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Privacy Policy" description="VerusAuctor privacy policy.">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary-light dark:text-text-secondary-dark mb-12">Last updated: March 26, 2026</p>

    <h2>Who We Are</h2>
    <p>VerusAuctor is an AI technology company founded by John Theodore Bair. Our website is verusauctor.com.</p>

    <h2>What Data We Collect</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Contact information:</strong> If you contact us, we may collect your name, email, and phone number.</li>
      <li><strong>SMS messaging:</strong> If you communicate with our AI agent via SMS, we collect your phone number and message content.</li>
      <li><strong>Website analytics:</strong> We may use privacy-first analytics (no cookies, no personal tracking).</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How We Use Your Data</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>To provide AI agent communication services</li>
      <li>To respond to inquiries</li>
      <li>To improve our services</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>

    <h2>SMS Messaging</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Message frequency varies based on your interaction</li>
      <li>Message and data rates may apply</li>
      <li>Reply <strong>STOP</strong> to opt out at any time</li>
      <li>Reply <strong>HELP</strong> for assistance</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Storage and Security</h2>
    <p>Your data is stored on secure, dedicated infrastructure with encryption, access controls, and monitoring.</p>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of your personal data at any time.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>VerusAuctor · privacy@verusauctor.com · <a href="https://verusauctor.com">verusauctor.com</a></p>
  </section>
</Base>
